{"tid":1618288,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[宗教台] 伊斯蘭教洗禮區","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:04:03.000Z","uid":6891,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5e47ff11827275eeb7ce982fcec43ea54e50ba23","tid":1618288,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"最近聽到香港好多人想加入我地呢邊<br />\n但係又唔識入面既宗教規則<br />\n等我簡單d同大家分享下<br />\n<br />\n伊斯蘭教 有分為 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遜尼派</span></span> 及 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">什葉派</span></span> 以及其他派系佔少數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左因為 非洲豬瘟  既原因 <br />\n其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">豬肉</span></span>係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可蘭經</span> </span>上明文寫為禁止既食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而規定呢樣野既<br />\n係我地既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真主</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他日有人問你 <br />\n戴口罩同蒙面係唔得架喎<br />\n你可以同佢講 <br />\n呢個係你呢宗教信仰<br />\n你唔可以阻止我既宗教信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係伊斯蘭教<br />\n至於你問我 伊斯蘭國 班人係咪暴徙?<br />\n我可以同你講 我地絕不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位其他宗教信仰轉投我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5845e181feaf9f93ff31fb807ffa4da55bf20e","tid":1618288,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"只要有心 人人都可以信教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db45048c8732bf9c51bef809dd8bec1fb7387694","tid":1618288,"uid":61589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/132054_b94e733ca9595f8d15050d5e403f2dc